@startuml
!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Context.puml

Person(apiUser, "API Client / User", "Web or mobile client, or external API consumer")
System(soccer, "Soccer Management System", "Microservices-based system for managing matches, leagues, teams and stadiums")
System(apiGateway, "API Gateway", "Single external entry point for all client traffic")
System(seedData, "Local Seed Data", "Packaged JSON seed files used for demo/local runs; no external API keys required")

Rel(apiUser, apiGateway, "Sends requests", "HTTPS/REST")
Rel(apiGateway, soccer, "Routes requests to internal services", "HTTP/REST")
Rel(soccer, seedData, "Loads local demo/seed data from", "Classpath JSON")

note right of apiGateway
API Gateway is the single external entry point for all clients.
Routes requests to the 4 backend services.
Works locally and in Docker using profile-specific upstream URLs.
end note

note right of soccer
System constraints:
- Match Service is the core orchestrator/data aggregator
- Each service owns its own PostgreSQL database
- Local testing uses H2
- Docker Compose uses PostgreSQL
- No service reads another service's database directly
- Demo mode uses local seed data only
- No external API keys are required
- Deployment uses 9 Docker containers
  (5 service containers + 4 PostgreSQL containers)
end note

@enduml
